    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build a thriving summer camp.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330570/extras/19cb4b4c7736143135cd4363e72bfcd5.poster.avif?t=1758221421\" width=600 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330570/extras/19cb4b4c7736143135cd4363e72bfcd5.webm?t=1758221421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330570/extras/19cb4b4c7736143135cd4363e72bfcd5.mp4?t=1758221421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to <strong>Camplandia</strong>! In this charming 2D build-em-up, you're tasked with creating and managing your very own summer camp. From designing cozy cabins to planning exciting activities, every decision you make shapes the success and reputation of your camp. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330570/extras/c807d28e85d836095be48b43e2e042f7.avif?t=1758221421\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Keep your campers happy and healthy.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330570/extras/9d27c782609207c9e4f6f68a94c469ac.poster.avif?t=1758221421\" width=600 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330570/extras/9d27c782609207c9e4f6f68a94c469ac.webm?t=1758221421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330570/extras/9d27c782609207c9e4f6f68a94c469ac.mp4?t=1758221421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start by constructing essential facilities. The campers are going to need beds to sleep in, showers to stay clean, and a cafeteria to keep their bellies full. But meeting their basic needs is just the beginning. Organize fun activities to keep your campers entertained like fishing, kayaking, and campfires. Hire staff to handle cooking, cleaning, and keep everything running smoothly. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330570/extras/c807d28e85d836095be48b43e2e042f7.avif?t=1758221421\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bring your dream summer camp to life.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330570/extras/239d01538351b2294422787b271e0063.poster.avif?t=1758221421\" width=600 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330570/extras/239d01538351b2294422787b271e0063.webm?t=1758221421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330570/extras/239d01538351b2294422787b271e0063.mp4?t=1758221421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Provide unforgettable experiences to earn glowing reviews and grow your camp. Whether you build by the beach, deep in the forest, or atop a snowy mountain, unlock new technologies and customize every detail to reflect your vision. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330570/extras/c807d28e85d836095be48b43e2e042f7.avif?t=1758221421\" width=600 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Will you build a summer camp paradise… or end up with a bug-infested disaster?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330570/extras/ea7737948db1ee61872b43c16610310d.poster.avif?t=1758221421\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330570/extras/ea7737948db1ee61872b43c16610310d.webm?t=1758221421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330570/extras/ea7737948db1ee61872b43c16610310d.mp4?t=1758221421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
